{"tid":113492,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇做Marketing 嘅冗員? 有關前路問題","createTime":"2017-02-09T04:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T07:28:30.000Z","uid":27433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"656d102f414532a84bd24526dfa85713997ed34e","tid":113492,"uid":27433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩出黎做野<br />\n做緊In house marketing， 但In house 真係比較少野做<br />\n我就真係唔多野做, 有少少覺得晒緊時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有少少想試下其他行業嘅marketing<br />\n之前見過幾份工, 人工還可以, 但都係典型香港公司, 福利差<br />\n<br />\n有冇做緊MNC marketing， 或其他中小型公司marketing 嘅巴絲講下前景，人工各方面俾小弟參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aad0e7fd8af850854a5f6f8fe962eaa1cb8f0d9","tid":113492,"uid":74109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"出黎agency一齊做狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddb5be9b4f96267a2b9551328b574d4ba05f463","tid":113492,"uid":27433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出黎agency一齊做狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgency 係咪真係有返工， 冇收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc91d288de5f31537e38cb1bc083690a872eefe","tid":113492,"uid":27433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}